<item chapterid="610508" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1955" articlename="婚外迷情" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521897933" lastupdate="1521897933" chaptername="第096章节我们有缘" chapterorder="96" size="6139" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    丁老师打断了我和沈晴的谈话，她说：“原来你们认识啊！”

